<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Webcam Capture</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../../../stylesheets/add_readings/style_ai.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</head>
<body>
 
    <article class="wrapper m-1 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-start">

        <!-- (A) VIDEO LIVE FEED -->
        <section>
        <video id="kam-live"  class="img-fluid img-thumbnail " autoplay></video>
        <div class="marker  text-center">take in this region - push "photo" below </div>
        </section>
        <!--decoded text-->
       <section class="main_content d-flex justify-content-center align-items-start flex-column px-3">
         
        <!-- (C) CONTROLS -->
        
        <div id="kam-controls" class="m-1 d-flex flex-column"> 
            <button id="kam-take" class="btn btn-primary m-1" >
                 photo.. 
            </button>
           
            <button  class="btn btn-primary m-1 d-none" id="recognize-results" >
                 recognize..
                 <span class="spinner-border progress_ spinner-border-sm d-none" role="status" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
             <a class="btn btn-primary  m-1 final_lnk   d-none" id="save-results" href="https://yahoo.com">Next step..</a>
            <!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary m-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop">
 Help..
</button>

            <!-- Modal -->
            <div class="modal fade m-1" id="staticBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="staticBackdropLabel">How to use</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                     <p>Please take a picture (IMPORTANT:digits of a counter must be in the red bar) for the recognition. After this push"recognize".
                     The taken picture appears below.When the taken picture is not good - take one more time.To correct reconized text - simple edit it.
                     Finally push "next step.."</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                   
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>

        </div>
                 

         <form action="" class="form" >
            <div class="m-0">
                <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label">your readings:</label>
                <input type="text" class="w-100 m-0 form-control decoded" name="readings" id="readingsofcounter" placeholder="123">
                <input class="estate_id" name="estate_id" type="number"  hidden>
                <input class="counter_id" name="counter_id" type="number"  hidden>
                
                
            </div>
        </form>
        <!-- (B) SNAPSHOTS -->
        <div id="kam-snaps" class="m-1"  >
            
        </div>
        <h6 class="h6 m-1">Your previous readings is: <%= previous %></h6>
        </section>


        <div class="position-fixed bottom-0 end-0 p-3" style="z-index: 11">
            <div id="liveToast" class="toast hide"  >
                <div class="toast-header">
                <img src="..." class="rounded me-2" alt="...">
                <strong class="me-auto text text-danger">Bootstrap</strong>
                <small>11 mins ago</small>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" ></button>
                </div>
                <div class="toast-body">
               No any data in the input, or not digits! Please take->recognize one more time, or enter data manually
                </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </article>
   <script src="../../../../javascripts/new_readings/step_ai.js">
    </script>
</body>
</html>
